idence >= pair.arbitrage_confidence`\\n3. **Direction Validation:** Signal direc
tion must match `pair.direction`\\n4. **Contract Sizing:** Suggest `contracts = 
min(100, max(1, risk_budget / price))`\\n\\n**Cooldown Key Generation:**\\n```cp
