d | 100% line coverage |\\n| Signal Generator | cooldown, confidence gate, direc
tion filter | 100% line coverage |\\n| Risk Manager | all pre-trade checks, circ
uit breaker, edge cases | 100% line coverage |\\n| Order Router | serialization,
retry logic, timeout handling | 100% line coverage |\\n| Position Tracker | open
