n    return std::string(buf, n);\n}\n```\n\n**Paired Order Submission:**\n```cpp
\nstd::pair<OrderResult, OrderResult> submit_paired(const PairedOrder& order) {\
n    auto result_a = submit_with_retry(order.leg_a, order.max_retries);\n    if 
